CREATE PROCEDURE [TCDTgt].[pr_SQS4_TCD_Order] @TRANSACTIONDATE VARCHAR(100)
AS
BEGIN
	SELECT 
		OrderID,
		OrderDetailID,
		ProductID,
		OrderQty,
		UnitPrice,
		LineTotal,
		TransactionDate,
		IdentifyTag
	INTO TCDTgt.SQS4_TCD_Order
	FROM TCSrc.SQS_Order
	WHERE CONVERT(DATE, TransactionDate, 103) >= CONVERT(DATE,@TRANSACTIONDATE,103)
END
